verbose_text: We performed the rescue assay using 2TC22C ES cells described above and found that amphioxus SoxB1, ascidian Ci-SoxB1 and fly SoxN possess the ability to support self-renewal of Sox2-null ES cells.
evidence: amphioxus SoxB1, ascidian Ci-SoxB1 and fly SoxN possess the ability to support self-renewal of Sox2-null ES
